snippet.title: Johnny Depp, Amber Heard Divorce Is Now A Tragic Soap Opera
snippet.description:
Amber Heard and Johnny Depp are officially broken up this week as the couple filed divorce papers. The writing was on the wall when Johnny Depp attended the 'Alice Through the Looking Glass' alone and Amber Heard was spotted looking very depressed while walking through LAX. Johnny Depp's mother also died and that is only the beginning of this sad story.
